The paper deals with the analysis of citation profiles of scientific papers in the computer science domain. The categories of citation profiles identified in the paper are relevant to several sub-fields of computer science such as information retrieval (cs.IR), digital libraries (cs.DL), social networks (cs.SI), cyber-physical systems (cs.CY), and software engineering (cs.SD). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
